sentence: Ivan Osorio is a senior policy analyst, columnist and editor at the Competitive Enterprise Institute (CEI) in Washington, D.C.
Before joining CEI, he wrote articles and policy studies for the Capital Research Center.
His work is regularly published in conservative, libertarian, and free-market periodicals such as National Review, Human Events, and the American Spectator.
